cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.GR 

This paper deals with face attribute manipulation using deep learning techniques, specifically Variational AutoEncoder (VAE) and Generative Adversarial Network (GAN). The paper focuses on image generation and modification, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category. Additionally, the use of VAE and GAN involves training and optimization, which are also relevant to the machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. The paper also deals with image processing and graphics (cs.MM) and the generation of facial masks for background consistency (cs.GR).
